description: The Heavenly Donut Truck known as "Dough Rider" provides donuts and coffee in Birmingham. We offer 10-12 flavors each day on the truck that include Maple Bacon, Oreo, Sour Cream Old-Fashioned, Apple Fritters and Red Velvet. Can't visit our truck?  Visit our store on Cahaba River Road for 35 flavors of donuts. We even make beignets on Saturday mornings from 7am-12noon
name: The Heavenly Donut Company
